# Specification Change Markers Workflow

Apply this when working in requirement specifications under `spec/requirements/*.md`.

- Support `[[ADD]]`, `[[REPLACE]]`, `[[DELETE]]`, and `[[NOTE]]` markers.
- Keep edits focused to marked regions and preserve heading hierarchy/status labels unless explicitly requested.
- Remove all markers after integration.
